The FDA also said it would ban imports until Huahai Pharmaceuticals discovered how the impurities were created and improved its quality control system.
Huahai Pharmaceutical issued a statement on the company's website on September 29, saying: "The company is taking a positive attitude and effective measures to rectify the problems existing in the official inspection of the United States and Europe, and the company is very surprised and regretful about the handling methods and results of the official inspection of the United States and Europe.
