In the past, at present, and in the future, China will neither copy foreign models, nor will it ask other countries to copy China's practices.
Earlier, when Wang Yi met with former US Secretary of State Henry Kissinger in New York, he said that Sino-US cooperation will be a win-win situation, and confrontation will inevitably be a lose-lose situation.
